  "description": "OHM, ORPHICA, OBBLIGATO, OTTONI, and OLE — all five Constellation engines in one room. Hippy Dad jam, microsound harp, dual wind, triple brass, and Afro-Latin trio. The fastest-built family in XOceanus history, now gathered for their first group portrait. The gathering — all five Constellation siblings in warm acoustic register. Sage, seafoam, coral, patina, hibiscus.",
